10 - autowire примитивных типов 

Через xml:
<bean class="com.Toyota">
        <constructor-arg ref="AA"/>
        <property name="ownerName" value="D.I."/>
    </bean>
    <bean id = "AA" class="com.BestFm"/>

configuration on
componentScan Of  

Or
configuration of
componentScan on
and in class toyota @autowired Radio & @Value ownerName

Or set from setter
